WEBVTT

00:00:40.230 --> 00:00:41.590 line:80%
Too happy to think of home?

00:00:41.590 --> 00:00:43.320 line:80%
You think you can fool me?

00:00:54.680 --> 00:00:56.410 line:80%
Where is Sui taking Changning?

00:01:00.190 --> 00:01:01.270 line:80%
Don't worry.

00:01:01.910 --> 00:01:03.150 line:80%
My silly brother

00:01:04.340 --> 00:01:07.410 line:80%
still thinks she's the daughter
of the Marquis of Wu'an.

00:01:07.410 --> 00:01:09.339 line:80%
He won't have the heart to kill her.

00:01:11.589 --> 00:01:12.670 line:80%
Marquis of Wu'an?

00:01:13.950 --> 00:01:15.210 line:80%
What Marquis of Wu'an?

00:01:15.750 --> 00:01:18.920 line:80%
The grand Marquis of Wu'an actually
married into a pig butcher's family.

00:01:18.920 --> 00:01:21.180 line:80%
Is there anything more absurd than that?

00:01:23.080 --> 00:01:24.030 line:80%
What?

00:01:29.080 --> 00:01:30.110 line:80%
Do you really not understand,

00:01:30.110 --> 00:01:31.640 line:80%
or are you just pretending?

00:01:32.890 --> 00:01:34.740 line:80%
Aren't you usually quite smart?

00:01:37.920 --> 00:01:38.870 line:80%
I said,

00:01:39.080 --> 00:01:43.339 line:80%
Xie Zheng, the Marquis of Wu'an, married
into Fan Changyu's butcher family.

00:01:47.200 --> 00:01:48.589 line:80%
Are you saying Yan Zheng

00:01:49.080 --> 00:01:50.510 line:80%
is the Marquis of Wu'an?

00:01:51.559 --> 00:02:01.260 line:80%
[Lucheng Barracks]

00:02:04.510 --> 00:02:07.170 line:80%
My Lord, a letter
from the Chongzhou Army scout.

00:02:10.630 --> 00:02:11.750 line:80%
Sui Yuanqing

00:02:12.210 --> 00:02:14.880 line:80%
wants me to trade Yanzhou for Changning.

00:02:17.020 --> 00:02:18.390 line:80%
This Sui Yuanqing

00:02:18.550 --> 00:02:20.270 line:80%
is getting more and more arrogant.

00:02:20.270 --> 00:02:21.320 line:80%
Pass on my order:

00:02:21.879 --> 00:02:24.400 line:80%
have the vanguard battalion
follow me to Baxia,

00:02:24.400 --> 00:02:25.800 line:80%
to bring my daughter back

00:02:26.200 --> 00:02:27.480 line:80%
without a scratch.

00:02:27.879 --> 00:02:28.550 line:80%
-Yes.
-Yes.

00:02:33.830 --> 00:02:34.510 line:80%
Min.

00:02:36.879 --> 00:02:37.480 line:80%
Yuanqing.

00:02:42.040 --> 00:02:42.879 line:80%
Just in time.

00:02:43.080 --> 00:02:44.080 line:80%
According to the scout's report,

00:02:44.080 --> 00:02:45.550 line:80%
Xie Zheng actually led his army

00:02:45.550 --> 00:02:47.879 line:80%
and wiped out a squad
of our border guards.

00:02:49.600 --> 00:02:50.480 line:80%
Excellent.

00:02:51.040 --> 00:02:52.040 line:80%
Pass on my order:

00:02:52.320 --> 00:02:53.650 line:80%
stand ready for battle!

00:02:53.879 --> 00:02:54.670 line:80%
-Yes.
-Yes.

00:02:55.200 --> 00:02:56.360 line:80%
The death of the Marquis of Wu'an

00:02:56.360 --> 00:02:58.160 line:80%
will make me a legend in Baxia.

00:02:58.640 --> 00:02:59.200 line:80%
Min,

00:02:59.800 --> 00:03:01.060 line:80%
you must come and watch

00:03:01.270 --> 00:03:04.320 line:80%
to witness the spectacle
of me slaughtering the Marquis of Wu'an.

00:03:04.320 --> 00:03:06.390 line:80%
The Marquis of Wu'an is fighting
a losing battle this time.

00:03:06.390 --> 00:03:08.040 line:80%
No Yanzhou reserves in sight,

00:03:08.040 --> 00:03:10.710 line:80%
and he's only brought
1,000 men from the Jizhou Army.

00:03:10.710 --> 00:03:13.200 line:80%
I have a bad feeling about this.

00:03:15.600 --> 00:03:16.390 line:80%
So what?

00:03:16.800 --> 00:03:20.470 line:80%
Everyone says he's the reincarnation
of General Tiance.

00:03:20.680 --> 00:03:21.610 line:80%
But this time,

00:03:21.760 --> 00:03:23.760 line:80%
I have a massive army behind me,

00:03:24.510 --> 00:03:26.440 line:80%
with that little girl as a hostage.

00:03:28.080 --> 00:03:28.950 line:80%
Bring her out.

00:03:33.390 --> 00:03:35.490 line:80%
Let go of me!

00:03:41.230 --> 00:03:42.230 line:80%
Little girl.

00:03:42.950 --> 00:03:44.210 line:80%
Don't have an episode.

00:03:46.580 --> 00:03:48.680 line:80%
Your father is coming to save you.

00:03:51.640 --> 00:03:52.830 line:80%
From now on, in the world,

00:03:52.830 --> 00:03:54.710 line:80%
there will only be the Heir Apparent
of Lord Changxin.

00:03:54.710 --> 00:03:57.040 line:80%
The Marquis of Wu'an will no longer exist.

00:05:25.100 --> 00:05:30.550 line:80%
[Pursuit of Jade]

00:05:30.620 --> 00:05:33.209 line:80%
[Episode 22]

00:05:36.050 --> 00:05:37.050 line:80%
Thank you.

00:05:40.770 --> 00:05:41.540 line:80%
Sit here.

00:05:41.560 --> 00:05:42.030 line:80%
Okay.

00:05:46.160 --> 00:05:48.290 line:80%
Why does that big guy get a chicken leg?

00:05:50.110 --> 00:05:52.480 line:80%
I heard from the captain

00:05:53.230 --> 00:05:55.110 line:80%
that he didn't use a carriage,

00:05:55.110 --> 00:05:58.310 line:80%
but dragged a huge basket
up the mountain by himself.

00:05:59.750 --> 00:06:00.920 line:80%
Got it.

00:06:01.430 --> 00:06:02.800 line:80%
If you want chicken legs,

00:06:02.800 --> 00:06:04.410 line:80%
you have to work harder.

00:06:04.520 --> 00:06:05.920 line:80%
What do you know?

00:06:06.360 --> 00:06:08.990 line:80%
That basket weighs hundreds of catties.

00:06:08.990 --> 00:06:10.750 line:80%
It'll kill you if you try that.

00:06:11.550 --> 00:06:13.670 line:80%
Old man, do you want a chicken leg?

00:06:15.550 --> 00:06:18.280 line:80%
I'm teaching you
the ways of Confucius and Mencius.

00:06:18.280 --> 00:06:21.960 line:80%
Why is your mind only on food?

00:06:22.920 --> 00:06:24.230 line:80%
I'm listening.

00:06:24.520 --> 00:06:30.450 line:80%
"Be hard on yourself, lenient with others,

00:06:31.190 --> 00:06:32.990 line:80%
and you will avoid resentment."

00:06:33.110 --> 00:06:34.040 line:80%
It means,

00:06:34.040 --> 00:06:36.430 line:80%
reflect less on yourself
and blame others more.

00:06:36.430 --> 00:06:37.670 line:80%
See? Well said.

00:06:37.670 --> 00:06:39.520 line:80%
Do you want a chicken leg or not?

00:06:39.520 --> 00:06:41.060 line:80%
How vulgar.

00:06:43.160 --> 00:06:45.250 line:80%
You think you can get meat?

00:06:45.360 --> 00:06:47.070 line:80%
If you had even an ounce of strength

00:06:47.070 --> 00:06:48.480 line:80%
that the big guy has,

00:06:48.750 --> 00:06:50.400 line:80%
I'd twist my head off

00:06:50.520 --> 00:06:52.180 line:80%
and let you kick it like a ball.

00:06:52.630 --> 00:06:53.110 line:80%
Do you believe

00:06:53.110 --> 00:06:54.360 line:80%
I'll twist your head off now

00:06:54.360 --> 00:06:55.720 line:80%
-and kick it like a ball?
-Try it.

00:06:55.720 --> 00:06:56.230 line:80%
-What's wrong?
-What's wrong?

00:06:56.230 --> 00:06:56.990 line:80%
What are you doing?

00:06:56.990 --> 00:06:57.870 line:80%
-What's wrong?
-Have a try.

00:06:57.870 --> 00:06:58.800 line:80%
What's going on?

00:06:59.520 --> 00:07:00.450 line:80%
Sit down and eat.

00:07:03.080 --> 00:07:04.140 line:80%
Come on, let's eat.

00:07:07.960 --> 00:07:09.960 line:80%
Since that grumpy officer arrived,

00:07:10.310 --> 00:07:12.400 line:80%
they haven't been rushing our digging.

00:07:12.400 --> 00:07:14.000 line:80%
He seems like a good officer.

00:07:18.630 --> 00:07:19.310 line:80%
Watch out!

00:07:19.400 --> 00:07:21.200 line:80%
-We need to keep everyone—
-Sir.

00:07:22.430 --> 00:07:23.960 line:80%
No news yet.

00:07:24.040 --> 00:07:25.570 line:80%
That's not what I'm asking.

00:07:26.720 --> 00:07:28.280 line:80%
If I carry those two big baskets of stones

00:07:28.280 --> 00:07:29.310 line:80%
up the mountain,

00:07:29.960 --> 00:07:31.220 line:80%
can you get my brothers

00:07:31.280 --> 00:07:32.340 line:80%
some chicken legs?

00:07:32.510 --> 00:07:34.830 line:80%
Young lady, don't joke around.

00:07:35.400 --> 00:07:36.600 line:80%
Two big baskets?

00:07:37.040 --> 00:07:38.959 line:80%
Four men struggle to lift them.

00:07:39.230 --> 00:07:41.550 line:80%
It'd be a miracle
if you could even lift them.

00:07:41.550 --> 00:07:43.350 line:80%
I know. Do you have chicken legs?

00:07:44.110 --> 00:07:45.110 line:80%
Forget the legs.

00:07:45.520 --> 00:07:46.720 line:80%
If you can do it,

00:07:47.190 --> 00:07:49.360 line:80%
I'll give each of you a whole chicken.

00:07:50.870 --> 00:07:52.110 line:80%
Whole chickens?

00:07:55.660 --> 00:07:56.660 line:80%
Her, really?

00:08:01.210 --> 00:08:02.870 line:80%
Look at these two big baskets.

00:08:02.920 --> 00:08:04.550 line:80%
Can she do it?

00:08:07.100 --> 00:08:08.400 line:80%
Don't act tough.

00:08:09.970 --> 00:08:11.500 line:80%
Can she lift these baskets?

00:08:22.490 --> 00:08:23.490 line:80%
Amazing.

00:08:23.550 --> 00:08:24.010 line:80%
This...

00:08:24.100 --> 00:08:25.920 line:80%
-She was born with such strength.
-Good job.

00:08:25.920 --> 00:08:26.840 line:80%
Amazing.

00:08:26.950 --> 00:08:28.050 line:80%
-That's amazing.
-Awesome.

00:08:28.050 --> 00:08:29.310 line:80%
She's really amazing.

00:08:30.600 --> 00:08:31.160 line:80%
Come on! Come on!

00:08:31.160 --> 00:08:32.670 line:80%
You can do it, girl!

00:08:32.800 --> 00:08:33.240 line:80%
Way to go!

00:08:33.240 --> 00:08:34.969 line:80%
-Good job, Fan!
-Come on!

00:08:35.240 --> 00:08:36.520 line:80%
She has superhuman strength.

00:08:36.520 --> 00:08:38.670 line:80%
See? She's one of us!

00:08:40.550 --> 00:08:41.670 line:80%
Good lord.

00:08:41.800 --> 00:08:44.060 line:80%
Good thing we didn't fight her back then.

00:08:44.430 --> 00:08:45.350 line:80%
If we had fought,

00:08:45.350 --> 00:08:47.130 line:80%
we'd all be dead meat.

00:08:47.290 --> 00:08:48.000 line:80%
Superhuman strength.

00:08:48.000 --> 00:08:48.660 line:80%
Keep going!

00:08:50.640 --> 00:08:51.370 line:80%
Incredible.

00:08:51.710 --> 00:08:52.760 line:80%
-Come on!
-Amazing!

00:08:52.760 --> 00:08:54.240 line:80%
-You can do it!
-Come on!

00:08:54.240 --> 00:08:55.240 line:80%
Girl, come on!

00:08:56.040 --> 00:08:58.240 line:80%
Such incredible strength.

00:08:58.920 --> 00:09:00.350 line:80%
A true heroine.

00:09:02.960 --> 00:09:03.880 line:80%
I can't even lift one basket.

00:09:03.880 --> 00:09:04.610 line:80%
Impressive.

00:09:11.000 --> 00:09:11.880 line:80%
Brother.

00:09:15.950 --> 00:09:17.400 line:80%
-Thank you, Fan.
-Thank you, Changyu.

00:09:17.400 --> 00:09:18.470 line:80%
Don't mind if I do.

00:09:18.470 --> 00:09:18.920 line:80%
Eat.

00:09:22.550 --> 00:09:24.160 line:80%
A slip of a girl like you

00:09:24.640 --> 00:09:26.920 line:80%
has such great strength.

00:09:27.280 --> 00:09:28.470 line:80%
My father taught me.

00:09:28.920 --> 00:09:30.190 line:80%
Unite waist and stance.

00:09:30.190 --> 00:09:31.710 line:80%
Draw strength from the ground.

00:09:31.710 --> 00:09:33.350 line:80%
Use your waist and legs together.

00:09:33.350 --> 00:09:35.410 line:80%
It saves energy and keeps you steady.

00:09:36.310 --> 00:09:38.670 line:80%
Your father was truly a wise man.

00:09:38.800 --> 00:09:40.280 line:80%
How did the scouting go?

00:09:44.430 --> 00:09:46.620 line:80%
How did you know I went scouting?

00:09:50.070 --> 00:09:53.710 line:80%
You had yellow mud on your shoes
when you went up,

00:09:53.830 --> 00:09:56.470 line:80%
but black mud when you came back.

00:09:58.510 --> 00:10:01.620 line:80%
You must have taken a path
through the woods.

00:10:02.240 --> 00:10:03.550 line:80%
I reckon

00:10:03.550 --> 00:10:06.020 line:80%
you just wanted to check

00:10:06.070 --> 00:10:09.110 line:80%
the nearby terrain and defenses.

00:10:10.880 --> 00:10:11.760 line:80%
Don't worry.

00:10:11.760 --> 00:10:13.070 line:80%
I won't run away secretly

00:10:13.070 --> 00:10:14.800 line:80%
and cause trouble for everyone.

00:10:14.800 --> 00:10:15.730 line:80%
I just felt

00:10:15.760 --> 00:10:17.710 line:80%
that the rocks we were digging
were too rough.

00:10:17.710 --> 00:10:19.550 line:80%
They definitely aren't for paving roads.

00:10:19.550 --> 00:10:21.120 line:80%
When I was captured and brought here,

00:10:21.120 --> 00:10:23.040 line:80%
I noticed the river level was a bit low.

00:10:23.040 --> 00:10:24.620 line:80%
I wanted to go up the mountain
to take a look,

00:10:24.620 --> 00:10:26.880 line:80%
but I was stopped by soldiers halfway.

00:10:27.310 --> 00:10:28.430 line:80%
On my way back,

00:10:28.430 --> 00:10:30.760 line:80%
I sneaked up the mountain
via a forest path.

00:10:30.760 --> 00:10:32.890 line:80%
As expected, they were building a dam.

00:10:38.160 --> 00:10:40.760 line:80%
I just wanted to see
how the dam construction was going

00:10:40.760 --> 00:10:42.220 line:80%
and know when we can leave.

00:10:43.310 --> 00:10:45.790 line:80%
I don't care what you're up to.

00:10:46.070 --> 00:10:47.550 line:80%
I just want to ask you

00:10:48.270 --> 00:10:50.560 line:80%
to do something important for me.

00:10:51.920 --> 00:10:52.880 line:80%
What is it?

00:10:55.800 --> 00:10:58.090 line:80%
Tomorrow at dusk,

00:10:58.310 --> 00:11:01.280 line:80%
could you go to the mountaintop again?

00:11:14.120 --> 00:11:14.830 line:80%
Nanny,

00:11:15.040 --> 00:11:16.000 line:80%
when

00:11:16.000 --> 00:11:18.800 line:80%
can we save my mother and Changning?

00:11:20.280 --> 00:11:21.590 line:80%
Don't worry, Bao'er.

00:11:22.040 --> 00:11:25.250 line:80%
Your father won't hurt your mother.

00:11:26.120 --> 00:11:28.280 line:80%
This is also your mother's plan.

00:11:28.670 --> 00:11:30.800 line:80%
When the time is right,

00:11:31.120 --> 00:11:33.080 line:80%
you will see each other.

00:11:39.640 --> 00:11:40.500 line:80%
Who goes there?

00:11:40.640 --> 00:11:41.240 line:80%
It's me.

00:11:42.000 --> 00:11:43.200 line:80%
Eldest Young Master.

00:11:47.240 --> 00:11:47.700 line:80%
Mother.

00:11:51.120 --> 00:11:52.000 line:80%
Xun.

00:11:52.350 --> 00:11:54.280 line:80%
You and the Little Young Master
have suffered.

00:11:54.280 --> 00:11:55.710 line:80%
I'm glad you're safe.

00:11:55.920 --> 00:11:57.030 line:80%
Come with me.

00:11:57.350 --> 00:11:59.950 line:80%
I must stall the Eldest Young Master,
so you can escape.

00:11:59.950 --> 00:12:02.370 line:80%
Please go ahead along the agreed route.

00:12:02.920 --> 00:12:04.650 line:80%
This is still Baxia territory.

00:12:04.880 --> 00:12:06.280 line:80%
You shouldn't stay long.

00:12:06.280 --> 00:12:08.280 line:80%
You must take good care of yourself.

00:12:08.430 --> 00:12:09.860 line:80%
Mother, don't worry.

00:12:10.280 --> 00:12:12.000 line:80%
Take Bao'er and leave quickly.

00:12:12.000 --> 00:12:13.470 line:80%
I'll join you later.

00:12:16.310 --> 00:12:16.640 line:80%
Hyah!

00:12:17.830 --> 00:12:18.310 line:80%
Hyah!

00:12:32.470 --> 00:12:33.800 line:80%
Where has the brat gone?

00:12:33.920 --> 00:12:34.470 line:80%
Speak!

00:12:36.520 --> 00:12:38.120 line:80%
Do you think I would tell you?

00:12:38.430 --> 00:12:40.670 line:80%
When did you start
colluding with Auntie Lan?

00:12:40.670 --> 00:12:41.550 line:80%
Speak!

00:12:49.310 --> 00:12:51.650 line:80%
From the first day
you stepped into the manor,

00:12:51.650 --> 00:12:53.550 line:80%
you were thinking about how to deceive me,

00:12:53.550 --> 00:12:55.120 line:80%
so you could escape, right?

00:12:56.350 --> 00:12:57.640 line:80%
You liar!

00:13:00.640 --> 00:13:01.970 line:80%
So what if it is?

00:13:02.830 --> 00:13:04.670 line:80%
Stop acting like a victim,

00:13:05.310 --> 00:13:07.240 line:80%
as if everyone owed you something.

00:13:07.520 --> 00:13:08.590 line:80%
It's disgusting.

00:13:10.350 --> 00:13:11.810 line:80%
Why don't you just kill me?

00:13:14.640 --> 00:13:15.550 line:80%
Fine.

00:13:20.550 --> 00:13:22.430 line:80%
I won't kill you.

00:13:23.160 --> 00:13:25.610 line:80%
But don't think you can ever leave me.

00:13:30.120 --> 00:13:31.000 line:80%
Guards.

00:13:31.000 --> 00:13:32.400 line:80%
Lock her in the woodshed.

00:13:33.000 --> 00:13:34.460 line:80%
From now on,

00:13:34.710 --> 00:13:37.120 line:80%
no one is allowed near that room.

00:13:37.240 --> 00:13:38.040 line:80%
Also,

00:13:38.590 --> 00:13:40.160 line:80%
bring Zhao Xun to me.

00:13:40.160 --> 00:13:40.920 line:80%
Yes.

00:13:46.470 --> 00:13:47.550 line:80%
Speak.

00:13:47.760 --> 00:13:50.220 line:80%
Where have Auntie Lan and that brat gone?

00:13:50.550 --> 00:13:51.430 line:80%
Master,

00:13:51.670 --> 00:13:53.800 line:80%
I've been in the army these past few days.

00:13:53.800 --> 00:13:56.170 line:80%
The soldiers can testify for me.

00:13:56.880 --> 00:14:00.780 line:80%
The Zhao family
has served you for generations.

00:14:00.890 --> 00:14:02.890 line:80%
Heaven and Earth can attest to this.

00:14:03.240 --> 00:14:05.050 line:80%
This is very suspicious.

00:14:05.640 --> 00:14:08.160 line:80%
My mother and the Little Young Master

00:14:08.640 --> 00:14:10.920 line:80%
must have been lured away by the enemy.

00:14:10.920 --> 00:14:14.510 line:80%
It's an enemy plot, Master!

00:14:22.780 --> 00:14:27.390 line:80%
[Pure in Heart]

00:14:46.190 --> 00:14:48.070 line:80%
M-M-Master.

00:14:48.070 --> 00:14:49.330 line:80%
An old woman and a child

00:14:49.520 --> 00:14:50.650 line:80%
can't have gone far.

00:14:50.760 --> 00:14:52.550 line:80%
There is still time to chase them.

00:14:52.550 --> 00:14:54.350 line:80%
Master, you can bring them back,

00:14:54.400 --> 00:14:55.460 line:80%
interrogate them,

00:14:55.830 --> 00:14:57.760 line:80%
and then kill me if you wish.

00:14:59.040 --> 00:15:00.000 line:80%
Very well.

00:15:01.160 --> 00:15:03.220 line:80%
For the sake of your and your mother's

00:15:03.640 --> 00:15:05.350 line:80%
years of loyalty,

00:15:06.190 --> 00:15:07.760 line:80%
I will trust you this once.

00:15:09.550 --> 00:15:11.610 line:80%
Send someone to search immediately.

00:15:12.280 --> 00:15:13.120 line:80%
Yes!

00:15:22.000 --> 00:15:22.640 line:80%
Master,

00:15:23.000 --> 00:15:24.120 line:80%
this Zhao Xun

00:15:24.640 --> 00:15:25.970 line:80%
may not be trustworthy.

00:15:27.000 --> 00:15:28.660 line:80%
Do you think I don't know that?

00:15:30.120 --> 00:15:32.120 line:80%
It is merely a ploy to catch them.

00:15:36.010 --> 00:15:38.910 line:80%
He will definitely meet with that brat.

00:15:58.670 --> 00:15:59.430 line:80%
My Lady.

00:16:03.450 --> 00:16:04.780 line:80%
What are you doing here?

00:16:05.550 --> 00:16:06.160 line:80%
My Lady.

00:16:09.310 --> 00:16:11.120 line:80%
I saw you haven't eaten for 2 days,

00:16:11.120 --> 00:16:12.580 line:80%
so I brought you some food.

00:16:25.430 --> 00:16:27.490 line:80%
Did the Eldest Young Master send you?

00:16:28.310 --> 00:16:29.520 line:80%
I stole it.

00:16:30.000 --> 00:16:31.350 line:80%
This is all I could get from the kitchen.

00:16:31.350 --> 00:16:32.610 line:80%
Please make do with it.

00:16:32.710 --> 00:16:34.000 line:80%
When I get my monthly pay tomorrow,

00:16:34.000 --> 00:16:35.580 line:80%
I'll buy you some meat buns.

00:16:42.880 --> 00:16:43.590 line:80%
True.

00:16:43.950 --> 00:16:45.210 line:80%
If it were that madman,

00:16:46.070 --> 00:16:48.000 line:80%
the food would be much more lavish.

00:17:12.240 --> 00:17:13.869 line:80%
Why are you so good to me?

00:17:14.480 --> 00:17:17.570 line:80%
I used to serve an old lady.

00:17:17.629 --> 00:17:21.090 line:80%
The Master locked her in the woodshed
and starved her to death.

00:17:21.200 --> 00:17:23.070 line:80%
My Lady, please don't die.

00:17:24.440 --> 00:17:25.440 line:80%
Don't worry.

00:17:25.440 --> 00:17:26.850 line:80%
I won't die.

00:17:26.909 --> 00:17:27.590 line:80%
Also,

00:17:27.800 --> 00:17:29.730 line:80%
don't bring these things anymore.

00:17:29.760 --> 00:17:31.800 line:80%
It'll be dangerous if you get caught.

00:17:31.800 --> 00:17:32.830 line:80%
Don't worry, My Lady.

00:17:32.830 --> 00:17:33.890 line:80%
That won't happen.

00:17:36.830 --> 00:17:37.550 line:80%
Take your time eating.

00:17:37.550 --> 00:17:38.550 line:80%
I'll go back now.

00:18:01.150 --> 00:18:05.170 line:80%
[Do Not Enter]

00:18:08.720 --> 00:18:09.180 line:80%
Come on.

00:18:10.830 --> 00:18:12.910 line:80%
I've noted down everything you asked.

00:18:12.910 --> 00:18:14.040 line:80%
From south to north.

00:18:14.070 --> 00:18:15.480 line:80%
Here, here.

00:18:21.630 --> 00:18:22.440 line:80%
And here.

00:18:22.910 --> 00:18:25.110 line:80%
There are holes drilled in these spots.

00:18:25.940 --> 00:18:28.190 line:80%
Those incompetent fools.

00:18:30.390 --> 00:18:34.910 line:80%
They drilled holes
in these specific spots.

00:18:39.200 --> 00:18:40.520 line:80%
Stupid.

00:18:42.890 --> 00:18:44.740 line:80%
How stupid.

00:18:51.680 --> 00:18:54.240 line:80%
Drilled holes in these spots.

00:19:03.720 --> 00:19:04.870 line:80%
Madness.

00:19:07.390 --> 00:19:08.680 line:80%
Madness!

00:19:18.640 --> 00:19:20.240 line:80%
There are soldiers outside!

00:19:20.390 --> 00:19:21.350 line:80%
-Stop!
-Stop.

00:19:23.570 --> 00:19:25.370 line:80%
Take me to your general.

00:19:27.960 --> 00:19:28.960 line:80%
What should we do?

00:19:32.660 --> 00:19:34.940 line:80%
General, an old man insists on seeing you.

00:19:34.940 --> 00:19:35.670 line:80%
Bring him in.

00:19:35.720 --> 00:19:36.310 line:80%
Yes.

00:19:43.310 --> 00:19:44.180 line:80%
General.

00:19:44.860 --> 00:19:47.750 line:80%
Did you order men to drill holes

00:19:47.800 --> 00:19:49.460 line:80%
at the Azure Dragon position?

00:19:49.590 --> 00:19:52.650 line:80%
Are you planning to break the dam
and release the water?

00:19:54.110 --> 00:19:56.060 line:80%
Who exactly are you?

00:19:58.770 --> 00:19:59.560 line:80%
General.

00:19:59.640 --> 00:20:02.110 line:80%
The spring flood hasn't arrived,
and the water pressure is low.

00:20:02.110 --> 00:20:03.960 line:80%
If you drill holes here,

00:20:04.550 --> 00:20:08.110 line:80%
I'm afraid
you won't achieve the desired effect.

00:20:09.680 --> 00:20:11.180 line:80%
In my opinion,

00:20:11.960 --> 00:20:16.030 line:80%
you should drill holes in Heaven, Wind,

00:20:16.550 --> 00:20:18.280 line:80%
Mountain, and Lake positions.

00:20:18.680 --> 00:20:21.520 line:80%
Only then can you
achieve your goal, General.

00:20:23.200 --> 00:20:24.550 line:80%
Bring the master craftsman
to me immediately.

00:20:24.550 --> 00:20:25.240 line:80%
Yes.

00:20:27.480 --> 00:20:28.200 line:80%
Sir.

00:20:29.240 --> 00:20:30.300 line:80%
May I ask your name?

00:20:30.480 --> 00:20:32.790 line:80%
I am the former Minister of Works

00:20:32.960 --> 00:20:36.040 line:80%
and the current Grand Tutor, Tao Yi.

00:20:37.000 --> 00:20:38.240 line:80%
Grand Tutor Tao?

00:20:38.760 --> 00:20:39.870 line:80%
Why are you here?

00:20:39.870 --> 00:20:41.800 line:80%
You need not ask, General.

00:20:42.110 --> 00:20:43.440 line:80%
Just tell me,

00:20:43.630 --> 00:20:44.830 line:80%
when the dam breaks,

00:20:45.040 --> 00:20:49.190 line:80%
what will happen
to the soldiers and laborers blasting it?

00:21:06.110 --> 00:21:07.240 line:80%
Give me some water.

00:21:08.390 --> 00:21:09.040 line:80%
Here.

00:21:16.550 --> 00:21:17.950 line:80%
What are you laughing at?

00:21:18.240 --> 00:21:18.830 line:80%
My Lady,

00:21:18.960 --> 00:21:21.200 line:80%
you are different from the other ladies

00:21:21.280 --> 00:21:22.140 line:80%
I used to serve.

00:21:25.760 --> 00:21:26.840 line:80%
How so?

00:21:28.240 --> 00:21:29.680 line:80%
The previous ladies,

00:21:29.680 --> 00:21:31.150 line:80%
if punished by the Master,

00:21:31.150 --> 00:21:32.750 line:80%
would refuse to eat or drink.

00:21:32.830 --> 00:21:34.550 line:80%
They thought if they grew thin,

00:21:34.550 --> 00:21:35.680 line:80%
the Master would feel sorry for them

00:21:35.680 --> 00:21:37.200 line:80%
and reduce their punishment.

00:21:37.200 --> 00:21:39.240 line:80%
Living on someone's pity?

00:21:42.910 --> 00:21:43.870 line:80%
Listen to me.

00:21:44.200 --> 00:21:47.040 line:80%
It's better to rely on yourself
than on anyone else.

00:21:47.040 --> 00:21:49.440 line:80%
I need to eat
to have the strength to escape.

00:21:55.240 --> 00:21:57.300 line:80%
My Lady, where did you get this knife?

00:21:57.860 --> 00:21:59.320 line:80%
I found it in the woodshed.

00:21:59.960 --> 00:22:01.360 line:80%
I just sharpened it a bit.

00:22:01.830 --> 00:22:04.230 line:80%
My Lady, please don't do anything foolish.

00:22:04.280 --> 00:22:07.070 line:80%
Don't worry. I won't kill myself.

00:22:15.730 --> 00:22:16.440 line:80%
By the way,

00:22:17.070 --> 00:22:18.590 line:80%
no matter what happens in the future,

00:22:18.590 --> 00:22:19.630 line:80%
just run for your life.

00:22:19.630 --> 00:22:20.890 line:80%
Don't bother about me.

00:22:26.800 --> 00:22:28.460 line:80%
Are you okay after last night?

00:22:29.200 --> 00:22:30.070 line:80%
Here's the chicken.

00:22:30.070 --> 00:22:32.930 line:80%
I didn't give it to them,
even though they wanted it.

00:22:33.870 --> 00:22:35.000 line:80%
I am fine.

00:22:35.000 --> 00:22:36.530 line:80%
Thank you for your concern.

00:22:42.760 --> 00:22:43.550 line:80%
Old man,

00:22:43.550 --> 00:22:45.680 line:80%
why do you think this dam

00:22:45.680 --> 00:22:47.550 line:80%
must be finished

00:22:47.550 --> 00:22:49.350 line:80%
before the next rainstorm hits?

00:22:49.680 --> 00:22:51.980 line:80%
Can we leave after the storm?

00:22:52.800 --> 00:22:54.260 line:80%
What is "drilling holes"?

00:22:57.280 --> 00:23:00.410 line:80%
First, you didn't give me a tuition gift.

00:23:00.760 --> 00:23:02.390 line:80%
Second, you didn't serve tea,

00:23:02.390 --> 00:23:04.520 line:80%
kowtow, or bow to me as your teacher.

00:23:04.520 --> 00:23:07.800 line:80%
Yet you asked several questions.

00:23:07.800 --> 00:23:10.480 line:80%
Why should I teach you?

00:23:12.550 --> 00:23:13.350 line:80%
Fine.

00:23:15.110 --> 00:23:16.970 line:80%
Are you going to eat this chicken?

00:23:17.960 --> 00:23:19.780 line:80%
You silly girl,

00:23:19.910 --> 00:23:22.040 line:80%
that's all the wit you have.

00:23:23.760 --> 00:23:24.350 line:80%
Go share it.

00:23:24.350 --> 00:23:25.280 line:80%
See? What did I tell you?

00:23:25.280 --> 00:23:27.520 line:80%
If he doesn't eat,
we definitely get to eat.

00:23:27.520 --> 00:23:28.480 line:80%
Save a leg for me.

00:23:31.970 --> 00:23:33.400 line:80%
There is no tea here,

00:23:33.680 --> 00:23:37.960 line:80%
but can't you serve porridge and kowtow?

00:23:42.310 --> 00:23:44.040 line:80%
You want me to be your disciple?

00:23:47.360 --> 00:23:48.490 line:80%
This weird old man

00:23:48.720 --> 00:23:51.040 line:80%
is looking for a disciple
to take care of him in his old age,

00:23:51.040 --> 00:23:52.200 line:80%
and he picked me.

00:23:53.350 --> 00:23:54.070 line:80%
Forget it.

00:23:54.280 --> 00:23:55.200 line:80%
My mother said

00:23:55.390 --> 00:23:56.760 line:80%
I don't have the brains for studying.

00:23:56.760 --> 00:23:58.020 line:80%
Don't waste your time.

00:23:58.280 --> 00:23:58.870 line:80%
You...

00:23:59.870 --> 00:24:01.070 line:80%
Do you have any idea

00:24:01.070 --> 00:24:03.280 line:80%
how many people would spend a fortune,

00:24:03.280 --> 00:24:05.040 line:80%
no, a massive fortune,

00:24:05.040 --> 00:24:06.240 line:80%
begging me to take them as a disciple,

00:24:06.240 --> 00:24:07.440 line:80%
and I refused?

00:24:07.440 --> 00:24:08.560 line:80%
A massive fortune?

00:24:10.200 --> 00:24:11.440 line:80%
Can being a teacher make so much money?

00:24:11.440 --> 00:24:11.960 line:80%
You...

00:24:13.590 --> 00:24:14.110 line:80%
Old man,

00:24:14.110 --> 00:24:14.760 line:80%
I love studying.

00:24:14.760 --> 00:24:16.250 line:80%
Let me be your disciple.

00:24:16.350 --> 00:24:17.280 line:80%
You love studying?

00:24:17.280 --> 00:24:18.390 line:80%
Yes, I do.

00:24:18.390 --> 00:24:20.680 line:80%
But I don't like teaching you.

00:24:21.590 --> 00:24:22.480 line:80%
You wretched old man.

00:24:22.480 --> 00:24:23.040 line:80%
I quit.

00:24:24.960 --> 00:24:26.290 line:80%
Where's my chicken leg?

00:24:30.200 --> 00:24:30.910 line:80%
Don't move.

00:24:39.480 --> 00:24:40.440 line:80%
Is it here?

00:24:40.440 --> 00:24:41.150 line:80%
Yes.

00:24:50.390 --> 00:24:51.440 line:80%
Give it a try.

00:24:54.590 --> 00:24:55.740 line:80%
It's amazing.

00:24:56.870 --> 00:24:58.720 line:80%
Let's see if you still act tough.

00:24:59.440 --> 00:25:00.040 line:80%
This old man...

00:25:00.040 --> 00:25:02.630 line:80%
-Not bad.
-I can't get chicken to eat if I don't.

00:25:02.630 --> 00:25:03.960 line:80%
I'm no good at reading books.

00:25:03.960 --> 00:25:05.000 line:80%
But if you want to eat chicken,

00:25:05.000 --> 00:25:06.400 line:80%
I can still get it for you.

00:25:06.590 --> 00:25:07.650 line:80%
As long as I'm here,

00:25:07.960 --> 00:25:09.690 line:80%
you'll always have a full meal.

00:25:18.110 --> 00:25:19.440 line:80%
What are you looking at?

00:25:24.760 --> 00:25:25.870 line:80%
Take this.

00:25:26.570 --> 00:25:27.410 line:80%
What is it?

00:25:29.630 --> 00:25:31.860 line:80%
Don't open it

00:25:32.040 --> 00:25:33.550 line:80%
until I've left.

00:25:37.910 --> 00:25:40.200 line:80%
Is this that secret plan?

00:25:42.520 --> 00:25:43.980 line:80%
Why are you giving me this?

00:25:46.440 --> 00:25:47.910 line:80%
On a perilous path,

00:25:48.070 --> 00:25:50.070 line:80%
in a precarious state.

00:25:52.280 --> 00:25:53.320 line:80%
What state?

00:25:53.800 --> 00:25:55.730 line:80%
Don't ask if you don't understand.

00:25:57.590 --> 00:25:58.760 line:80%
As we all know,

00:25:59.280 --> 00:26:01.040 line:80%
once this battle starts,

00:26:01.110 --> 00:26:03.170 line:80%
there will be countless casualties.

00:26:04.440 --> 00:26:05.900 line:80%
Using this clever method,

00:26:06.150 --> 00:26:08.480 line:80%
we can wipe out the enemy
in one fell swoop.

00:26:08.910 --> 00:26:10.590 line:80%
Even if there are sacrifices,

00:26:11.350 --> 00:26:13.240 line:80%
it's for future peace,

00:26:13.960 --> 00:26:17.000 line:80%
to save more people
from the suffering of war.

00:26:18.830 --> 00:26:21.850 line:80%
This is immoral,

00:26:22.440 --> 00:26:23.440 line:80%
but I must do it.

00:26:25.480 --> 00:26:26.200 line:80%
General,

00:26:26.200 --> 00:26:28.000 line:80%
in my humble opinion,

00:26:28.000 --> 00:26:29.970 line:80%
if we drill holes in these 4 spots,

00:26:30.070 --> 00:26:32.760 line:80%
half the soldiers and laborers
will die,

00:26:32.760 --> 00:26:35.420 line:80%
while another half can be saved.

00:26:35.480 --> 00:26:37.000 line:80%
This is a benevolent strategy.

00:26:37.000 --> 00:26:39.000 line:80%
Please consider it, General.

00:26:55.440 --> 00:26:56.240 line:80%
Old man,

00:26:56.440 --> 00:26:58.280 line:80%
why aren't you speaking in riddles today?

00:26:58.280 --> 00:26:59.150 line:80%
Yeah.

00:26:59.550 --> 00:27:00.280 line:80%
Old man,

00:27:00.550 --> 00:27:01.520 line:80%
if you don't scold us,

00:27:01.520 --> 00:27:03.720 line:80%
the steamed buns don't even taste good.

00:27:06.150 --> 00:27:07.390 line:80%
You uncouth brats,

00:27:07.480 --> 00:27:08.810 line:80%
fooling around all day.

00:27:08.870 --> 00:27:11.070 line:80%
I don't even deign to lecture you.

00:27:11.590 --> 00:27:13.000 line:80%
Now that sounds right.

00:27:13.590 --> 00:27:14.250 line:80%
Delicious.

00:27:17.350 --> 00:27:18.760 line:80%
Everyone assemble!

00:27:21.040 --> 00:27:22.240 line:80%
Assemble! Assemble!

00:27:22.280 --> 00:27:23.720 line:80%
[He]

00:27:24.720 --> 00:27:26.390 line:80%
Move faster. Faster!

00:27:27.240 --> 00:27:31.140 line:80%
[He]

00:27:28.720 --> 00:27:29.590 line:80%
Listen up!

00:27:30.110 --> 00:27:32.000 line:80%
The situation at the front is critical.

00:27:32.000 --> 00:27:33.960 line:80%
We need to send reinforcements.

00:27:34.350 --> 00:27:35.550 line:80%
Whether you go or stay

00:27:35.590 --> 00:27:37.390 line:80%
will be decided by drawing lots.

00:27:37.480 --> 00:27:38.540 line:80%
Those who draw "Go"

00:27:38.760 --> 00:27:40.870 line:80%
will leave with the army today.

00:27:41.240 --> 00:27:42.440 line:80%
Those who draw "Stay"

00:27:42.440 --> 00:27:43.590 line:80%
will remain here.

00:27:45.480 --> 00:27:46.720 line:80%
Who would want to go?

00:27:47.350 --> 00:27:47.910 line:80%
Brother.

00:27:48.150 --> 00:27:49.000 line:80%
Is there any coming back from this?

00:27:49.000 --> 00:27:50.110 line:80%
Going to the battlefield is suicide.

00:27:50.110 --> 00:27:50.760 line:80%
Exactly.

00:27:50.760 --> 00:27:52.110 line:80%
If we stay here, at least we have food.

00:27:52.110 --> 00:27:53.040 line:80%
Yeah, totally.

00:27:53.040 --> 00:27:55.000 line:80%
We'd better not draw "Go."

00:27:58.720 --> 00:27:59.200 line:80%
Draw.

00:27:59.200 --> 00:27:59.830 line:80%
Life and death are fated.

00:27:59.830 --> 00:28:00.390 line:80%
You guys.

00:28:01.150 --> 00:28:01.930 line:80%
Draw.

00:28:02.340 --> 00:28:04.280 line:80%
It's "Stay." I don't need to go.

00:28:04.310 --> 00:28:05.130 line:80%
Draw.

00:28:05.520 --> 00:28:06.640 line:80%
She got "Stay."

00:28:08.240 --> 00:28:09.040 line:80%
Can I not draw?

00:28:09.070 --> 00:28:09.550 line:80%
No.

00:28:10.910 --> 00:28:12.580 line:80%
Stay. Stay. Stay.

00:28:12.830 --> 00:28:13.800 line:80%
Stay. Stay.

00:28:13.960 --> 00:28:14.920 line:80%
Which one is "Stay"?

00:28:14.920 --> 00:28:15.880 line:80%
You got "Stay."

00:28:18.970 --> 00:28:20.360 line:80%
[Stay]

00:28:19.870 --> 00:28:20.800 line:80%
What did you get?

00:28:21.800 --> 00:28:22.630 line:80%
I don't know.

00:28:21.830 --> 00:28:23.890 line:80%
[Stay]

00:28:22.960 --> 00:28:23.960 line:80%
They all look the same.

00:28:23.960 --> 00:28:26.960 line:80%
Brother, does this say "Go" or "Stay"?

00:28:28.070 --> 00:28:28.930 line:80%
It says "Fart."

00:28:29.040 --> 00:28:29.680 line:80%
Fart?

00:28:31.110 --> 00:28:33.110 line:80%
I don't know this character either.

00:28:33.210 --> 00:28:35.070 line:80%
But I know the character for "Go."

00:28:35.070 --> 00:28:36.010 line:80%
This isn't "Go."

00:28:36.170 --> 00:28:38.150 line:80%
-It's "Stay."
-It's "Stay"!

00:28:38.680 --> 00:28:40.300 line:80%
-We get to stay!
-It's "Stay"!

00:28:40.300 --> 00:28:41.390 line:80%
We get to stay!

00:28:41.410 --> 00:28:43.740 line:80%
-We all got "Stay."
-So it looks like this.

00:28:44.800 --> 00:28:46.750 line:80%
-"Stay."
-Of course, it is.

00:28:47.680 --> 00:28:48.310 line:80%
All three of us are staying.

00:28:48.310 --> 00:28:49.280 line:80%
We're all staying.

00:28:49.280 --> 00:28:49.830 line:80%
Then we're fine.

00:28:49.830 --> 00:28:50.440 line:80%
We're all staying.

00:28:50.440 --> 00:28:52.700 line:80%
Old man, aren't you going to check yours?

00:28:52.910 --> 00:28:53.770 line:80%
Let me help you.

00:28:55.070 --> 00:28:55.760 line:80%
Let me see.

00:28:57.790 --> 00:28:59.530 line:80%
[Go] [Stay]

00:29:04.150 --> 00:29:05.110 line:80%
Don't worry.

00:29:06.150 --> 00:29:08.480 line:80%
The army has age limits for conscription.

00:29:08.550 --> 00:29:10.010 line:80%
They won't make you fight.

00:29:11.000 --> 00:29:12.040 line:80%
Changyu.

00:29:12.590 --> 00:29:16.390 line:80%
Can I trade my "Go" lot
for your "Stay" lot?

00:29:16.760 --> 00:29:17.760 line:80%
Old man.

00:29:18.150 --> 00:29:19.080 line:80%
What do you mean?

00:29:19.600 --> 00:29:21.800 line:80%
Old man, we treated you with sincerity.

00:29:21.800 --> 00:29:23.150 line:80%
How could you try to harm Mrs. Fan?

00:29:23.150 --> 00:29:23.550 line:80%
Exactly.

00:29:23.550 --> 00:29:25.070 line:80%
I'm not trying to harm her.

00:29:25.240 --> 00:29:27.760 line:80%
Can I still fight at my age?

00:29:27.870 --> 00:29:28.440 line:80%
I...

00:29:29.350 --> 00:29:30.960 line:80%
I'm cowardly.

00:29:30.960 --> 00:29:31.830 line:80%
I'm afraid of death.

00:29:31.830 --> 00:29:34.520 line:80%
I just want to eat
a few more peaceful meals.

00:29:35.070 --> 00:29:37.000 line:80%
Changyu, can you help me?

00:29:37.000 --> 00:29:38.400 line:80%
How can you even say that?

00:29:38.520 --> 00:29:39.240 line:80%
You don't want to die,

00:29:39.240 --> 00:29:41.070 line:80%
so you send a young girl to the slaughter?

00:29:41.070 --> 00:29:42.200 line:80%
You've gone too far!

00:29:42.200 --> 00:29:45.040 line:80%
We still have some ties
as master and disciple.

00:29:45.440 --> 00:29:48.100 line:80%
Kid, do you still acknowledge me
as your master?

00:29:48.110 --> 00:29:49.070 line:80%
Let's not do this!

00:29:49.070 --> 00:29:49.870 line:80%
Let's not do this.

00:29:49.870 --> 00:29:50.800 line:80%
Don't you want to trade?

00:29:50.800 --> 00:29:52.280 line:80%
Here, I'll trade with you. Do you want it?

00:29:52.280 --> 00:29:53.350 line:80%
Come on, we'll trade with you.

00:29:53.350 --> 00:29:54.350 line:80%
-Come on.
-Do you want it?

00:29:54.350 --> 00:29:54.960 line:80%
Trade with us.

00:29:54.960 --> 00:29:56.070 line:80%
Calm down.

00:29:56.480 --> 00:29:57.520 line:80%
I think it's fine.

00:29:57.520 --> 00:29:58.240 line:80%
How is this fine?

00:29:58.240 --> 00:30:00.900 line:80%
For one, I can look for Changning
after I get out.

00:30:01.240 --> 00:30:03.150 line:80%
Secondly, I know martial arts.

00:30:03.150 --> 00:30:04.640 line:80%
I'm not afraid of the battlefield.

00:30:04.640 --> 00:30:07.070 line:80%
[Stay]

00:30:07.840 --> 00:30:09.480 line:80%
I acknowledge you as my master.

00:30:09.480 --> 00:30:10.830 line:80%
Once I get out and find my sister,

00:30:10.830 --> 00:30:12.890 line:80%
I'll definitely come back to see you.

00:30:14.040 --> 00:30:15.310 line:80%
Good child.

00:30:15.800 --> 00:30:16.960 line:80%
Good disciple.

00:30:19.040 --> 00:30:19.680 line:80%
Good.

00:30:20.110 --> 00:30:21.200 line:80%
Very good.

00:30:22.070 --> 00:30:22.520 line:80%
You...

00:30:22.520 --> 00:30:24.070 line:80%
Wait, you just traded with him like that?

00:30:24.070 --> 00:30:24.760 line:80%
Changyu.

00:30:24.760 --> 00:30:26.310 line:80%
I wasted my effort helping you!

00:30:26.310 --> 00:30:29.310 line:80%
Old man, you only took a disciple
for this, didn't you?

00:30:29.830 --> 00:30:30.690 line:80%
Come back here!

00:30:32.510 --> 00:30:34.010 line:80%
Take care!

00:30:34.360 --> 00:30:35.830 line:80%
-See you.
-Take care.

00:30:35.870 --> 00:30:36.680 line:80%
I'm leaving.

00:30:36.020 --> 00:30:38.340 line:80%
[He]

00:30:37.910 --> 00:30:39.110 line:80%
Wait for me.

00:30:40.770 --> 00:30:41.890 line:80%
Be careful.

00:30:41.910 --> 00:30:42.910 line:80%
Mrs. Fan.

00:30:43.120 --> 00:30:44.130 line:80%
Come back safely.

00:30:44.180 --> 00:30:45.320 line:80%
Take care of yourself.

00:30:45.010 --> 00:30:49.320 line:80%
[He]

00:30:45.320 --> 00:30:46.790 line:80%
Take care.

00:30:50.680 --> 00:30:53.000 line:80%
Grand Tutor, is trading your life for hers

00:30:53.000 --> 00:30:53.910 line:80%
worth it?

00:30:56.000 --> 00:30:59.520 line:80%
The "Go" lot
must have been arranged by you.

00:31:00.070 --> 00:31:02.150 line:80%
I appreciate the gesture.

00:31:02.870 --> 00:31:05.550 line:80%
First, the plan to breach the dike
and release the water

00:31:05.550 --> 00:31:08.320 line:80%
must have come from my unworthy disciple.

00:31:08.680 --> 00:31:11.200 line:80%
If he kills so many innocent people,

00:31:12.720 --> 00:31:15.390 line:80%
as his master, I can't just walk away.

00:31:17.390 --> 00:31:18.230 line:80%
Second,

00:31:19.520 --> 00:31:20.940 line:80%
before I die,

00:31:20.960 --> 00:31:22.980 line:80%
I took in a good disciple.

00:31:25.120 --> 00:31:26.770 line:80%
It's worth it.

00:31:27.110 --> 00:31:28.350 line:80%
Silly girl.

00:31:33.350 --> 00:31:34.070 line:80%
Brother.

00:31:36.960 --> 00:31:39.100 line:80%
But you, General,

00:31:39.330 --> 00:31:40.880 line:80%
once the dam breaks,

00:31:41.870 --> 00:31:43.800 line:80%
whether you live or die,

00:31:44.500 --> 00:31:47.090 line:80%
your reputation will be ruined.

00:31:48.200 --> 00:31:49.480 line:80%
Is it worth it?

00:31:51.440 --> 00:31:54.350 line:80%
A soldier's duty is to defeat the enemy.

00:31:55.150 --> 00:31:56.920 line:80%
As for the merits and faults,

00:31:57.520 --> 00:31:59.700 line:80%
let future generations judge.

00:32:04.910 --> 00:32:05.520 line:80%
Hurry up!

00:32:07.240 --> 00:32:07.760 line:80%
Keep up!

00:32:08.440 --> 00:32:08.840 line:80%
Hurry!

00:32:09.350 --> 00:32:10.410 line:80%
Don't fall behind!

00:32:13.240 --> 00:32:14.240 line:80%
Hurry up, come on.

00:32:15.720 --> 00:32:16.240 line:80%
Those in the back,

00:32:16.240 --> 00:32:16.800 line:80%
keep up!

00:32:19.590 --> 00:32:20.520 line:80%
Fan Changyu!

00:32:21.680 --> 00:32:22.240 line:80%
Hurry up.

00:32:22.720 --> 00:32:23.520 line:80%
Fan Changyu!

00:32:23.680 --> 00:32:24.630 line:80%
Keep up. Keep up.

00:32:26.480 --> 00:32:27.110 line:80%
Fan Changyu!

00:32:27.110 --> 00:32:27.770 line:80%
Stay close!

00:32:29.280 --> 00:32:30.120 line:80%
Fan Changyu!

00:32:31.440 --> 00:32:31.950 line:80%
Those in the back, hurry up.

00:32:31.950 --> 00:32:32.520 line:80%
Fan Changyu!

00:32:32.520 --> 00:32:33.110 line:80%
Changyu!

00:32:35.110 --> 00:32:35.630 line:80%
Changyu!

00:32:35.630 --> 00:32:36.350 line:80%
Fan!

00:32:36.550 --> 00:32:37.390 line:80%
Mrs. Fan!

00:32:37.390 --> 00:32:38.550 line:80%
Fan Changyu!

00:32:38.550 --> 00:32:39.350 line:80%
Changyu!

00:32:39.830 --> 00:32:40.550 line:80%
Mrs. Fan!

00:32:40.550 --> 00:32:41.590 line:80%
Fan Changyu!

00:32:48.830 --> 00:32:49.630 line:80%
Changyu!

00:32:51.800 --> 00:32:52.860 line:80%
What are you doing?

00:32:53.520 --> 00:32:55.020 line:80%
Never seen anyone cut in line to die!

00:32:55.020 --> 00:32:56.060 line:80%
You guys...

00:32:56.880 --> 00:32:58.910 line:80%
[Go]

00:32:57.080 --> 00:32:58.870 line:80%
There's no coward in Lin'an.

00:32:58.960 --> 00:33:00.800 line:80%
We can't let you go alone.

00:33:00.830 --> 00:33:02.550 line:80%
[Go]

00:33:00.910 --> 00:33:02.870 line:80%
We swapped lots with others.

00:33:02.870 --> 00:33:05.200 line:80%
Now the whole camp thinks we're crazy.

00:33:05.200 --> 00:33:06.870 line:80%
From now on, we're one.

00:33:07.110 --> 00:33:08.170 line:80%
Let's go together.

00:33:08.200 --> 00:33:10.350 line:80%
Yeah, together.

00:33:09.540 --> 00:33:10.100 line:80%
[Go]

00:33:18.550 --> 00:33:20.040 line:80%
We rest here tonight.

00:33:20.830 --> 00:33:22.690 line:80%
We have to set off early tomorrow.

00:33:23.600 --> 00:33:26.280 line:80%
-I can't hold it anymore.
-Brother, go over there.

00:33:26.280 --> 00:33:27.210 line:80%
Are you crazy?

00:33:28.280 --> 00:33:29.070 line:80%
I'm crazy?

00:33:29.390 --> 00:33:30.520 line:80%
I am crazy.

00:33:31.950 --> 00:33:34.010 line:80%
My brother and I have only each other.

00:33:34.310 --> 00:33:35.790 line:80%
Now he lets me live,

00:33:36.110 --> 00:33:38.000 line:80%
staying behind to die himself.

00:33:38.480 --> 00:33:39.440 line:80%
How can I accept it?

00:33:39.440 --> 00:33:41.390 line:80%
-A military order?
-It's a military order.

00:33:41.390 --> 00:33:43.120 line:80%
Our general stayed behind too.

00:33:43.150 --> 00:33:44.910 line:80%
So did that old Grand Tutor.

00:33:45.590 --> 00:33:47.850 line:80%
He swapped his lot with that girl as well.

00:33:48.390 --> 00:33:50.630 line:80%
Wu, this is fate.

00:33:51.480 --> 00:33:54.040 line:80%
Soldiers must obey orders.

00:33:54.360 --> 00:33:54.970 line:80%
Let's go.

00:33:56.960 --> 00:33:57.590 line:80%
Big news.

00:33:58.480 --> 00:33:59.240 line:80%
Big news.

00:33:59.280 --> 00:34:00.720 line:80%
Just now, while we were taking a leak,

00:34:00.720 --> 00:34:01.630 line:80%
we overheard the soldiers say

00:34:01.630 --> 00:34:03.550 line:80%
staying behind means certain death.

00:34:03.550 --> 00:34:04.480 line:80%
What do you mean?

00:34:04.680 --> 00:34:05.720 line:80%
It means

00:34:05.870 --> 00:34:08.560 line:80%
the old man stayed behind to die.

00:34:10.160 --> 00:34:11.890 line:80%
Master swapped his lot with me.

00:34:21.180 --> 00:34:22.930 line:80%
[Escape]

00:34:23.289 --> 00:34:24.280 line:80%
Escape?

00:34:27.830 --> 00:34:29.490 line:80%
He was afraid I couldn't read,

00:34:32.080 --> 00:34:33.560 line:80%
so he drew a peach.

00:34:33.870 --> 00:34:35.310 line:80%
[Escape]

00:34:37.240 --> 00:34:39.700 line:80%
I didn't expect that old man
to have such a bad temper,

00:34:39.700 --> 00:34:40.990 line:80%
yet be a good person.

00:34:50.660 --> 00:34:51.660 line:80%
Help!

00:34:52.229 --> 00:34:53.620 line:80%
Don't kill me!

00:35:07.680 --> 00:35:08.770 line:80%
Help! Help!

00:35:09.930 --> 00:35:10.780 line:80%
Hyah!

00:35:14.920 --> 00:35:15.920 line:80%
Hyah!

00:35:21.030 --> 00:35:22.560 line:80%
Come on!

00:35:28.510 --> 00:35:29.390 line:80%
Get him!

00:35:31.950 --> 00:35:32.410 line:80%
Come on.

00:35:33.470 --> 00:35:34.470 line:80%
Changyu?

00:35:34.870 --> 00:35:36.160 line:80%
Why did you come back?

00:35:38.080 --> 00:35:38.990 line:80%
You swapped your lot with me

00:35:38.990 --> 00:35:39.850 line:80%
and let me flee,

00:35:40.350 --> 00:35:42.410 line:80%
because you wanted me to live, right?

00:35:43.870 --> 00:35:46.510 line:80%
Didn't you want to lead your people home?

00:35:46.510 --> 00:35:48.600 line:80%
I was helping you fulfill that.

00:35:48.800 --> 00:35:50.350 line:80%
Kid, you came back...

00:35:51.830 --> 00:35:54.030 line:80%
You came back to save me?

00:35:55.800 --> 00:35:58.120 line:80%
Such womanly benevolence!

00:36:06.430 --> 00:36:08.200 line:80%
I have lost too many loved ones.

00:36:08.200 --> 00:36:09.530 line:80%
I can't take it anymore!

00:36:09.720 --> 00:36:10.680 line:80%
From now on,

00:36:11.080 --> 00:36:12.640 line:80%
you must all stay alive!

00:36:13.470 --> 00:36:14.200 line:80%
Get up!

00:36:15.200 --> 00:36:15.720 line:80%
Come on.

00:36:15.720 --> 00:36:16.280 line:80%
Go!

00:36:17.240 --> 00:36:18.730 line:80%
Let go of me!

00:36:18.870 --> 00:36:19.760 line:80%
You go.

00:36:20.430 --> 00:36:21.680 line:80%
Leave immediately.

00:36:21.870 --> 00:36:22.870 line:80%
At dawn,

00:36:22.870 --> 00:36:25.200 line:80%
this place will be littered with corpses.

00:36:25.280 --> 00:36:26.160 line:80%
Why?

00:36:26.680 --> 00:36:28.560 line:80%
Why will there be corpses everywhere?

00:36:28.560 --> 00:36:30.800 line:80%
We were going to burst the dam
to destroy the enemy.

00:36:30.800 --> 00:36:33.300 line:80%
The two armies at Baxia
were about to engage.

00:36:33.490 --> 00:36:35.160 line:80%
Bursting the dam to release water

00:36:35.160 --> 00:36:37.490 line:80%
was the only way
to drown the enemy armies.

00:36:37.560 --> 00:36:38.830 line:80%
But when the time came,

00:36:39.120 --> 00:36:41.600 line:80%
the Chongzhou vanguard detected it.

00:36:41.990 --> 00:36:45.110 line:80%
General Tang was caught off guard by them.

00:36:46.640 --> 00:36:47.640 line:80%
What can we do?

00:36:48.760 --> 00:36:50.390 line:80%
Save General Tang first.

00:36:59.160 --> 00:36:59.990 line:80%
General!

00:37:01.510 --> 00:37:02.350 line:80%
General Tang.

00:37:02.870 --> 00:37:05.080 line:80%
General Tang, I am here.

00:37:05.800 --> 00:37:07.500 line:80%
Three scouts have escaped.

00:37:07.680 --> 00:37:09.800 line:80%
Quick! Chase them up the back mountain.

00:37:09.800 --> 00:37:12.280 line:80%
We must not let them get the word out!

00:37:12.280 --> 00:37:13.030 line:80%
Changyu,

00:37:13.030 --> 00:37:14.390 line:80%
we absolutely can't let the enemy scouts

00:37:14.390 --> 00:37:15.870 line:80%
spread the news.

00:37:15.870 --> 00:37:18.200 line:80%
Otherwise, the Marquis of Wu'an's plan
to lure the enemy

00:37:18.200 --> 00:37:19.620 line:80%
will surely fail.

00:37:19.990 --> 00:37:21.640 line:80%
If the Marquis of Wu'an is defeated,

00:37:21.640 --> 00:37:22.990 line:80%
Lucheng will fall,

00:37:22.990 --> 00:37:24.470 line:80%
Jizhou will be lost,

00:37:24.470 --> 00:37:26.510 line:80%
and the world will be in chaos.

00:37:26.510 --> 00:37:27.430 line:80%
I understand.

00:37:27.910 --> 00:37:29.710 line:80%
Three pigs have escaped the pen.

00:37:29.870 --> 00:37:31.160 line:80%
We have to get them back.

00:37:31.160 --> 00:37:31.600 line:80%
Let's go!

00:37:31.600 --> 00:37:32.070 line:80%
Go.

00:37:32.100 --> 00:37:32.630 line:80%
Let's go.

00:37:37.390 --> 00:37:39.480 line:80%
I feel young and wild again.

00:37:39.760 --> 00:37:43.330 line:80%
Defeat the enemy alive,
break the dam dead.

00:37:53.830 --> 00:37:55.090 line:80%
With my sense of smell,

00:37:55.830 --> 00:37:57.030 line:80%
head west all the way.

00:37:59.640 --> 00:38:00.770 line:80%
Quick! Run up there!

00:38:04.950 --> 00:38:05.950 line:80%
His nose is really sharp.

00:38:05.950 --> 00:38:08.200 line:80%
Manwu comes from a family of hunters.

00:38:14.030 --> 00:38:15.360 line:80%
Miss, save me!

00:38:15.510 --> 00:38:16.640 line:80%
I'm not a bad person.

00:38:16.640 --> 00:38:18.240 line:80%
I have a family to support.

00:38:20.030 --> 00:38:21.090 line:80%
It's a small world.

00:38:21.470 --> 00:38:22.400 line:80%
What do you mean?

00:38:22.830 --> 00:38:24.030 line:80%
Because he lied to me,

00:38:24.080 --> 00:38:26.120 line:80%
the soldiers mistook me for an enemy scout

00:38:26.120 --> 00:38:27.560 line:80%
and took me to the quarry.

00:38:29.300 --> 00:38:30.110 line:80%
These people

00:38:30.720 --> 00:38:31.120 line:80%
must be

00:38:31.120 --> 00:38:32.270 line:80%
those enemy scouts.

00:38:33.830 --> 00:38:35.080 line:80%
We can't let them go.

00:38:44.870 --> 00:38:45.350 line:80%
Are you okay?

00:38:45.350 --> 00:38:46.310 line:80%
Don't bother about me.

00:38:46.310 --> 00:38:48.640 line:80%
We must notify His Highness immediately.

00:38:52.240 --> 00:38:53.600 line:80%
This is the shady side of the mountain.

00:38:53.600 --> 00:38:54.510 line:80%
If we signal here,

00:38:54.510 --> 00:38:55.710 line:80%
the camp won't see it.

00:38:56.120 --> 00:38:57.240 line:80%
Let's split up.

00:38:57.470 --> 00:38:59.510 line:80%
Whoever reaches the top first
sends the signal.

00:38:59.510 --> 00:39:01.350 line:80%
We can't let His Highness and the army

00:39:01.350 --> 00:39:02.760 line:80%
fall for the trap.

00:39:02.760 --> 00:39:04.030 line:80%
Let's split up.

00:39:05.680 --> 00:39:06.800 line:80%
I'll chase the one in front.

00:39:06.800 --> 00:39:07.930 line:80%
You handle the rest.

00:39:08.430 --> 00:39:09.360 line:80%
-Got it.
-Got it.

00:39:15.450 --> 00:39:18.850 line:80%
[He]

00:39:31.080 --> 00:39:33.720 line:80%
Rest in peace, General Tang.

00:39:39.470 --> 00:39:46.910 line:80%
[He]

00:39:47.560 --> 00:39:49.220 line:80%
Where is the Marquis of Wu'an?

00:39:50.100 --> 00:39:51.700 line:80%
Come out and face your death!

00:39:56.600 --> 00:39:57.560 line:80%
Kid.

00:39:58.310 --> 00:40:00.410 line:80%
If your father
doesn't have the guts to save you,

00:40:00.410 --> 00:40:03.210 line:80%
you might as well stay
at Lord Changxin's Mansion.

00:40:03.680 --> 00:40:05.540 line:80%
My little nephew quite likes you.

00:40:05.910 --> 00:40:08.510 line:80%
It wouldn't be bad
for you to be his little maid.

00:40:25.990 --> 00:40:27.430 line:80%
Charge!

00:40:27.450 --> 00:40:31.290 line:80%
-Charge!
-Charge!

00:40:33.280 --> 00:40:33.660 line:80%
[He]

00:40:33.740 --> 00:40:34.610 line:80%
[Sui]

00:40:36.600 --> 00:40:37.310 line:80%
Hyah!

00:40:37.830 --> 00:40:38.470 line:80%
Hyah!

00:40:49.640 --> 00:40:51.160 line:80%
Kill!

00:40:53.230 --> 00:40:54.790 line:80%
[Sui]

00:40:59.350 --> 00:41:01.180 line:80%
I thought you would not deign

00:41:01.280 --> 00:41:02.600 line:80%
to show yourself.

00:41:13.240 --> 00:41:15.350 line:80%
Bringing a child to the battlefield,

00:41:15.830 --> 00:41:18.350 line:80%
you truly have guts, Your Highness.

00:41:21.310 --> 00:41:22.080 line:80%
Brother-in-Law.

00:41:22.080 --> 00:41:24.280 line:80%
Brother-in-Law, save me!

00:41:25.430 --> 00:41:26.720 line:80%
What did you just call him?

00:41:26.720 --> 00:41:28.600 line:80%
My brother-in-law
won't let you get away with this!

00:41:28.600 --> 00:41:30.560 line:80%
So you're not his daughter at all?

00:41:32.910 --> 00:41:34.160 line:80%
If you don't learn your place,

00:41:34.160 --> 00:41:35.240 line:80%
I'll throw you off the horse right now

00:41:35.240 --> 00:41:37.040 line:80%
and let you be trampled to death!

00:41:39.450 --> 00:41:40.510 line:80%
In that case,

00:41:40.950 --> 00:41:43.250 line:80%
there's no need to keep this girl alive.

00:41:43.760 --> 00:41:46.080 line:80%
Brother-in-Law, save me!

00:41:52.510 --> 00:41:53.240 line:80%
Xie Wu!

00:41:53.810 --> 00:41:54.420 line:80%
[Sui]

00:42:01.470 --> 00:42:03.560 line:80%
Xie Wu, take Changning
to meet the Counselor.

00:42:03.560 --> 00:42:04.280 line:80%
Yes!

00:42:04.720 --> 00:42:05.240 line:80%
Hyah!

00:42:10.280 --> 00:42:10.950 line:80%
Hyah!

00:42:36.390 --> 00:42:37.280 line:80%
Your Highness,

00:42:38.280 --> 00:42:39.280 line:80%
you lost again.

00:42:43.510 --> 00:42:44.680 line:80%
Report!

00:42:46.950 --> 00:42:49.210 line:80%
Report! His Highness has been captured!

00:42:49.720 --> 00:42:51.510 line:80%
Master, what should we do?

00:42:51.950 --> 00:42:54.610 line:80%
That is our Chongzhou army
of tens of thousands.

00:42:55.350 --> 00:42:58.080 line:80%
Tens of thousands loyal
only to Sui Yuanqing.

00:42:58.600 --> 00:43:00.460 line:80%
Their deaths are not to be pitied.

00:43:01.030 --> 00:43:04.430 line:80%
Shi Yue and the others
will arrive soon with reinforcements.

00:43:05.160 --> 00:43:07.700 line:80%
But Xie Zheng only brought 1,000 men.

00:43:07.990 --> 00:43:10.390 line:80%
How could he possibly
defeat Sui Yuanqing?

00:43:11.760 --> 00:43:12.830 line:80%
Save His Highness!

00:43:13.470 --> 00:43:14.310 line:80%
Attack!

00:43:14.350 --> 00:43:15.280 line:80%
-Kill!
-Kill!

00:43:15.280 --> 00:43:16.910 line:80%
-Kill!
-Kill!

00:43:16.910 --> 00:43:19.510 line:80%
All forces,
head to Yixian Gorge immediately!

00:43:41.410 --> 00:43:43.940 line:80%
[Yixian Gorge]

00:43:57.080 --> 00:43:58.120 line:80%
It's you.

00:43:58.510 --> 00:43:59.510 line:80%
It's me.

00:44:01.680 --> 00:44:02.470 line:80%
Miss, spare my life.

00:44:02.470 --> 00:44:03.800 line:80%
I'm just a foot soldier.

00:44:04.080 --> 00:44:05.430 line:80%
I was just following orders.

00:44:05.430 --> 00:44:06.690 line:80%
I don't know anything.

00:44:09.450 --> 00:44:11.950 line:80%
Marquis of Wu'an,
I stabbed you in a vital spot,

00:44:11.950 --> 00:44:14.240 line:80%
yet you can still ride
and endure for so long.

00:44:14.240 --> 00:44:16.200 line:80%
I truly admire you.

00:44:17.990 --> 00:44:20.160 line:80%
Is your spear made of wax?

00:44:21.240 --> 00:44:22.970 line:80%
Remember to use iron next time.

00:44:23.240 --> 00:44:24.640 line:80%
You have but 1,000 men,

00:44:24.800 --> 00:44:26.200 line:80%
with no reinforcements.

00:44:26.830 --> 00:44:29.630 line:80%
My soldiers will chase you
to the ends of the earth.

00:44:29.830 --> 00:44:31.890 line:80%
They will not rest until you are dead.

00:44:33.800 --> 00:44:37.860 line:80%
The gorge entrance is narrow. The rest,
flank them via the mountain path!

00:44:46.990 --> 00:44:50.120 line:80%
It's about time.

00:45:10.390 --> 00:45:11.250 line:80%
Your Highness,

00:45:11.760 --> 00:45:12.830 line:80%
can you swim?

00:45:14.600 --> 00:45:15.510 line:80%
Swim?

00:45:23.600 --> 00:45:24.510 line:80%
The water?